The paper discusses a new class of computer that learns by itself and writes its own program to solve a problem, which suggests it belongs to the sub-category of neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of electromagnetic resonance bands and wireless communication, which could fall under the sub-categories of systems and control (cs.SY), embedded systems (cs.ET), and electromagnetics (cs.EM).
